Install Xcode CLI Tools and install HomeBrew

$ xcode-select --install
$ /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
$ brew install pkg-config libssh libxml2 curl pcre cmake
$ curl -O https://devhub.cisco.com/artifactory/osx-ydk/0.7.0/libydk-0.7.0-Darwin.pkg
$ sudo installer -pkg libydk-0.7.0-Darwin.pkg -target /

Install PIP

https://pip.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installing/

Install YDK Models
$ pip install ydk-models-cisco-ios-xr
$ pip install ydk-models-cisco-ios-xe
$ pip install ydk-models-openconfig
$ pip install ydk-models-ietf

Install LXML
brew unlink libxml2
brew unlink libxslt

Reference sites
http://ydk.cisco.com/py/docs/getting_started.html#macos
https://pip.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installing/
